    <div class="container" id="product">
        <h1>Our Product</h1>
        <h2>Chargin-out Phone Cases</h2>
        <p>Our phone cases are equipped with state-of-the-art technology that enables wireless power transfer between devices. Whether you're at home, in the office, or on the go, Chargin-out phone cases ensure that you always have power when you need it.</p>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Using advanced inductive and resonant coupling technologies, our phone cases can send and receive power wirelessly. Simply place two Chargin-out cases near each other, and watch as the power is seamlessly transferred from one device to another.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container" id="technology">
        <h1>Our Technology</h1>
        <h2>Wireless Charging</h2>
        <p>Our technology leverages the principles of inductive and resonant coupling to achieve efficient wireless power transfer. With built-in safety mechanisms and optimized power management, our phone cases provide a reliable and safe charging experience.</p>
        <h2>Safety and Efficiency</h2>
        <p>Chargin-out phone cases are designed with safety in mind. Over-voltage protection, over-current protection, and temperature regulation ensure that your devices are protected during the charging process. Our technology also maximizes efficiency, reducing energy loss and ensuring fast charging times.</p>
